{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1697-04_083","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"La Fauvette de Sapho au Moineau de Sylvie","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", avril 1697 [tome 4], p. 83-86.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Vous sçavez quelle gloire s’est acquise la Fauvette de la celebre Sapho. Il semble qu’elle se renouvelle toutes les années par le retour du Printemps. C’est ce qui a donné lieu à un jeune Gentilhomme de faire les Vers que vous allez lire.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"LA FAUVETTE","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[0]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"DE SAPHO","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"Au Moineau de Sylvie.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[4]/#"}}]}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Oiseaux avec envie","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Me regardent presque tous ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je fais de même de vous.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ah, vous estes à Sylvie.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Je ne commence mes chants","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que lors qu’on voit la verdure","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Renouveller la nature ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vos plaisirs sont de tout temps.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Chez Sapho dans un lieu sombre","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je me repose souvent.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chez Sylvie également,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous vous reposez à l’ombre.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Dans ses mains elle vous prend,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous carresse, vous embrasse,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vous y tenez la place","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du Dieu de tous le plus grand.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Si je puis oüir sans cesse","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Respirer les doux zephirs,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous entendez les soupirs","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De vostre jeune Maistresse.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Teste à teste, comme on sçait,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous avez droit de luy dire","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les sentimens qu’elle inspire,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ah, Moineau, c’est un secret.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Changeons de sort, de ma vie","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoi qu’on vante la douceur,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je ne compte pour bonheur","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que celui d’estre à Sylvie.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}}]}}}